## Ingredients

* 1 cup milk
* 1 tbsp cocoa powder
* 1 tbsp sugar
* sprinkle of ground cinnamon
* sprinkle of salt
* drops of vanilla extract
* marshmallows (optional)

## Instructions

1. Heat milk.
2. Stir in the seasonings
3. (Optional) Top with marshmallows
